# Mission ImmunoPossible: The Incredible World Inside You

**Find out how we can generate electricity from plants** - CBS Talk first given by Swetha Kannan in 2024

Last initially checked on 2024-02-04 by Swetha Kannan (sk2152@cam.ac.uk) and double-checked on 2024-02-22 by Chiara Delpiano-Cordeiro (cd796@cam.ac.uk)

**Frequency of use:** n/a

